Title   : de_odubookstore

Update

[1/05/08] I actually am publicly releasing this map, as the building it
            resembles no longer exists as depicted.  (So, we are lawsuit

[6/10/07] Added some missing textures to the BSP file and updated te NAV

===================================================

Description

Medium Sized Bomb Diffusal Map using various textures (thanks all authors)
and scripted sequences (inclusive pseudo-random scripting to give the
effect of a war zone).  The scene is inspired by my schools bookstore which
is part of its main campus building, albeit not perfectly replicated.  This
map tried to be as immersing as possible.  Enjoy!

=================================================== 

Construction

Geometry : 4 weeks (approx)
Entity   : 2 weeks (approx)
Scripting: 1 week  (approx) 

Total Builtime to completion:  2 months (approx)

=================================================== 

Installation 

1. Extract the .bsp file to your Counter-Strike Source map directory.

===================================================

Credits 

Special Thanks to playtester Serius305Playa of D$P for allowing me to
	play test this map on his server.  Hi-5.  Special thanks to the 
	architects of de_xcom for an inspiring level, and a lot of ideas
	came from.

Wow, after around a year and a half this map is finally done.  It seems that the recent updates actually helped this map.  I was finally able to generate a nav file an the map overall runs alot better then about 6 months ago.

Anyway, the map is as optimized as I could get it, its pretty hard with a map this size, but I didn't get below 100fps in any area, however older computers will probably not be able to run this.

There are two bombsites, one in the factory near the middle of the map, and one in the main floor of the observatory (the room with the tesla things in it).

Again, the map does include a nav file to play around with bots, and a custom radar image to help you find where you are going.

I was going to add more screens, but they were too big to upload at the best quality, so you can see more screens from older stages to get more of an idea of the map.

Novaewas initially one of the few greatRomanlegionary fortresses along the empire's border, forming part of the defences (limes Moesiae) along theDanubein northernBulgaria. The settlement later expanded into a town in the Roman province ofMoesia Inferior, later Moesia Secunda.It lies about 4km east of the modern town ofSvishtov.

**de _ nostria _ b1**
==================
<iframe width="440" height="235" src="http://www.youtube.com/embed/5C_t7vTQi0E" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>
_Available in 720p._

Counter-Terrorists: Prevent Terrorists from bombing chemical weapon crates. Team members must defuse any bombs that threaten targeted areas.

Terrorists: The Terrorist carrying the C4 must destroy one of the chemical weapon stashes.

Background: Terrorists in the middle east are planning on blowing up yet another chemical weapons storage facility that will devastate the local area and its inhabitants due to the fallout of chemicals from the explosion.

**Features**
==================
- HDR (Tonemap Controller used)
- Soundscape (Indoors and Outdoors)
- Optimisation
- 3d skybox
- Overview / Radar
- Detail
- 64 spawn points

Installation
==================
To install, unpack the .rar file to:

"Steam\steamapps\USERNAME\counter-strike source\cstrike\maps"

Comment & Rate
==================  
Please give constructive feedback and rate.
This is the beta release. I tried to fix as many bugs as possible. But there might be some spots that I forgot to add a playerclip brush for example. Please tell me so I can fix that for the next release.
I worked on this map with alot of dedication and I hope you guys like it.

Have Fun !
